{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_06_01",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタイン前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します\n{user}さんにお話があります",
      "startTime": 4.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん？　どうかしたのか",
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あー、また鈴村さん言うて、他人行儀やわ～\nうちと{user}さんの仲やんかぁ",
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば下の名前で呼ぶ約束だったな\n分かったよ、ゆ……優……",
      "startTime": 21.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "んー、まだぎこちないなぁ\nもっとはっきり言ってもらわんと聞こえへんよ",
      "startTime": 29.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ、優\n……これでいいか？",
      "startTime": 35.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……下の名前で呼ぶの、早く慣れて下さいね",
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "今度間違えたら、罰として吐息多めな甘く囁くイケボで\nうちの名前を呼んでもらいますからね",
      "startTime": 48.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっと聞いてみたいかも……",
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "勘弁してくれ……\nそれより俺に用事があるんじゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 57.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。今日はトリエルの鈴村優ではなく\n瑠依ちゃんの唇守り隊隊長として言わせてもらいます",
      "startTime": 64.5999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのお力で\n瑠依ちゃんのCMのキスシーンをなくして下さい",
      "startTime": 71.3999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺にそんな権限はないよ\nそれに、まだ諦めてなかったのか……",
      "startTime": 77.8333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前です。瑠依ちゃんがどこの馬の骨とも\n分からん男とキスするなんて、うちが許しません",
      "startTime": 84.5999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんは責任感の強い子やから\nやりたないことでも多少のことなら我慢してしまいます",
      "startTime": 91.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど、我慢出来るだけで傷つかない訳やないんよ\n傷ついても「大丈夫」言うて平気な顔をする子なんよ",
      "startTime": 101.4333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなん誰かが守ってあげなあかんやろ？\nせやから、瑠依ちゃんのことは親友のうちが守るんです",
      "startTime": 110.3666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。でもここは俺に任せてくれないか\n瑠依を傷つけるようなことは絶対にしないと約束する",
      "startTime": 119.2666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのことは信用してます\nせやけど心配な気持ちは抑えられへんの",
      "startTime": 126.4666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "今も暇さえあればキスを阻止する方法を考えてしもて\nそのうち相手の役者さんを尾行して闇討ちしそうやわ",
      "startTime": 135.799994405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "頼むから尾行はしないでくれよ？　だが、そうだな……\nそういうことなら一つ頼みを聞いてくれないか？",
      "startTime": 147.7666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.5333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.5333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ここにあるのは、トリエルが歌うバレンタイン楽曲の\n歌詞とデモテープだ",
      "startTime": 156.8666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "この歌詞を読み込んで\n優なりの解釈を瑠依とすみれに伝えてくれないか",
      "startTime": 160.2666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.9666610717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "それは構いませんけど、なんでうち一人なん？\n……はは～ん、そういうことですか",
      "startTime": 169.3666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.8666610717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "うちを忙しくさせて、瑠依ちゃんのこと\n考えさせへんつもりやろ",
      "startTime": 176.5333277384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "そうはいかへんよ、こんなんでうちが\n瑠依ちゃんのことを忘れる訳ないやんか",
      "startTime": 182.4666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.6333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "もう狙いを見抜かれたか……\nだが、優に依頼した理由はそれだけじゃないぞ",
      "startTime": 188.499994405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "今度の曲は恋のときめきや学校での青春といった要素が\n大事になる。そういう意味では瑠依やすみれは……",
      "startTime": 195.7666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.1333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "……せやね。甘酸っぱい青春や恋のときめきは\n瑠依ちゃんやすみれちゃん向きちゃうなぁ",
      "startTime": 205.2333277384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "それなら二人にはうちの解釈を伝えた方が\nイメージを掴みやすいかもしれへんね",
      "startTime": 212.0333277384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.999994405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはそこまで考えて\nうちに提案したんやな。さすがやわ",
      "startTime": 217.599994405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 221.5333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、CMのことばかり考えてる訳にもいかんし\n他ならぬ{user}さんの頼みやもんなぁ",
      "startTime": 226.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.699994405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nうちなりに歌詞を読み込んで二人に伝えてみます",
      "startTime": 231.1333277384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "startTime": 235.9333277384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
